{"tid":902813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公投 會打飛機嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2018-11-15T05:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T06:17:15.000Z","uid":94097,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"967a9175939069eade7b8f1cb437cf6018ab9fba","tid":902813,"uid":94097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早一兩日成班仔食緊宵夜果時咁啱講起打飛機嘅話題。其中一個男仔話平時佢射果時唔會用紙巾接住，而係由佢射係自己個身到。我哋其他人聽到眼都凸。想問下巴打們平時打飛機係點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用張紙巾係巨龍頭準備接精<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 射係自己個身到 之後再用紙巾擦返"},{"pid":"33d9efa52a19e6b52309b6199c2f221e200735e3","tid":902813,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0b048bcb251d43df203ca5a63e28b8bad989b59","tid":902813,"uid":41992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:33:11.000Z","msg":"射入口 當水飲唔好浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455814795a28974b66a5d43af1668eb1ddad3619","tid":902813,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"插自己屎忽內射自己"}]}